- `tests/unit/v182_multi_position_validation.test.ts` (6 tests) — pins server-side enforcement: SOCCER accepts `CB/CM`, REJECTS `FIXO`/`DF`; FUTSAL accepts `FIXO/PIVOT`, REJECTS `CB`/`ST`/`FW`; empty `positions[]` accepted (matches legacy "no position recorded").

