### Out of scope (queued for follow-ups)

- Formation viz (item 1a) — `MatchdayAvailability.tsx`'s `pickFormation` can survive this PR by reading the JOINED positions string (e.g. `"DF/MF"`) which the public-data mapper produces from `positions.join('/')`. The hybrid switch already handles that shape.
- Wholesale "edit-details" page redesign (item 2).
- Per-position fee resolver — `LeaguePositionFee` stays single-string-keyed; resolver picks the FIRST positions[] entry as the "primary" for fee matching. Documented but not enabled for futsal codes (no real futsal league has fees set today).
